---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Download Your AI OS Quick Start Guide | Nova Labs"
  description="Build your first AI skill in 10 minutes. A practical guide to setting up Claude Code as your business operating system."
>
  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-40 bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-surface-lighter/30">
    <div class="section-container flex items-center justify-between py-4">
      <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        <span class="text-primary-light">Nova</span><span class="text-text-dim">Labs</span>
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
        <a href="/#pricing" class="btn-primary !py-2.5 !px-5 !text-sm">
          Get the full playbook
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-20 pb-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-success/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-container relative z-10 max-w-2xl text-center">
      <!-- Success icon -->
      <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-success/15 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black leading-tight mb-4 tracking-tight">
        Your Quick Start Guide is ready
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-text-muted mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Build your first AI skill in 10 minutes. Open the guide and follow the 4 steps.
      </p>

      <!-- Download button -->
      <a href="/AI-OS-Blueprint-Free-Preview.pdf" download class="btn-primary text-lg inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
        </svg>
        Download Quick Start Guide (PDF)
      </a>

      <!-- What's next -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 text-left mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">What you'll build</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/15 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-light font-bold text-sm">1</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Set up your AI OS project</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Create the folder structure that turns Claude Code into a business system. Takes 2 minutes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/15 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-light font-bold text-sm">2</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Teach the AI your business</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Write one context file. From that point on, every AI interaction knows your voice, audience, and what you do.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/15 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-light font-bold text-sm">3</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Build a content writing skill</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Create a reusable skill that writes LinkedIn posts, blogs, and social content in YOUR voice. No code.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-success/15 flex items-center justify-center text-success font-bold text-sm">4</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Try it and see the difference</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Run your skill. The output sounds like you, not like AI. That's the power of a system vs. scattered prompts.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Social proof / stats -->
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-center">
        <div class="px-4">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-light">92+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-dim">pages of content</p>
        </div>
        <div class="px-4">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-light">12</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-dim">chapters in the playbook</p>
        </div>
        <div class="px-4">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-light">30 days</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-dim">of real-world testing</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Skill Pack CTA - entry offer -->
      <div class="mt-10 p-8 rounded-2xl border-2 border-success/30 bg-success/5 relative">
        <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-success text-surface text-xs font-bold px-4 py-1 rounded-full">QUICK START</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Skip the setup. Start producing.</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">You just learned how to build one skill. Get 5 production-ready skills that work out of the box: content writer, email triage, meeting prep, daily planner, weekly review.</p>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6 text-sm">Drop them in your project folder. Run Claude Code. Done. No configuration needed.</p>

        <a href="https://novalabs-ai.lemonsqueezy.com/checkout/buy/42602dd3-c435-4294-88d2-d871f76ff5c6" class="btn-primary checkout-link text-lg" data-value="9" data-product="skillpack">
          Get the Skill Pack - $9
        </a>

        <p class="text-sm text-text-dim mt-4">Instant download. 30-day money-back guarantee. No risk.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Full system CTA -->
      <div class="mt-6 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Want the full system?</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">The complete playbook: 12 chapters covering architecture, memory, automation, and the Nova Labs case study. Plus clone-ready repo and all 5 skills.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-warning mb-6">Launch price ends April 18. Regular price: $67.</p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="https://novalabs-ai.lemonsqueezy.com/checkout/buy/142170b8-348f-42fa-aa57-5954f195e266" class="btn-secondary checkout-link" data-value="47" data-product="playbook">
            Get the Playbook - $47
          </a>
          <a href="https://novalabs-ai.lemonsqueezy.com/checkout/buy/e686f7b7-1b44-4454-b67b-20fc86a31a85" class="btn-secondary checkout-link" data-value="97" data-product="bundle">
            Get the Bundle - $97
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-text-dim mt-4">30-day money-back guarantee. One-time payment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="py-12 border-t border-surface-lighter/30">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div class="text-center md:text-left">
          <p class="text-text-dim text-sm">
            <span class="text-primary-light font-semibold">Nova Labs</span> - AI-powered business tools by AckNova Automations
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-text-dim">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Playbook</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Blog</a>
          <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Terms</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!-- Conversion tracking for free chapter signup -->
  <script>
    if (typeof gtag === 'function') {
      gtag('event', 'generate_lead', {
        'currency': 'USD',
        'value': 0,
        'event_category': 'free_chapter'
      });
    }
  </script>
</Layout>
